23:41.477 --> 23:45.436
Our Father in Heaven...
Before we go into battle...

23:45.548 --> 23:47.448
Every soldier among us
will approach you...

23:47.550 --> 23:48.448
...each in his own way.

23:50.486 --> 23:53.455
Our enemies too according
to their own understanding...

23:53.556 --> 23:56.457
...will ask for protection and
for victory.

23:56.559 --> 23:59.460
And so we bow before your
infinite wisdom.

23:59.562 --> 24:02.395
We offer our prayers
the best we can.

24:03.432 --> 24:07.459
l pray you watch over the young
men like Jack Geoghegan...

24:07.570 --> 24:09.401
...that l lead into battle.

24:10.439 --> 24:12.999
You use me as your instrument
in this awful hell...

24:13.109 --> 24:14.406
...of war to watch over them.

24:16.445 --> 24:19.414
