this one beside me...

24:19.515 --> 24:22.416
...deserving of a future in your
blessing and good will.

24:23.452 --> 24:25.420
-Amen.
-Amen.

24:27.456 --> 24:30.425
Oh, yes... and one more
thing, Dear Lord...

24:30.526 --> 24:32.426
...about our enemies...

24:34.096 --> 24:36.656
...ignore their heathen prayers
and help us blow...

24:36.766 --> 24:39.428
...those little bastards
straight to hell.

24:39.535 --> 24:40.433
Amen again.

24:42.471 --> 24:43.438
Amen.

24:44.473 --> 24:45.440
Thank you.

24:47.943 --> 24:50.434
There is one about the kid
with the apple tree...

24:50.546 --> 24:52.446
