and stuff on him.

24:55.551 --> 24:57.451
-Daddy.
-Yes?

24:57.553 --> 24:59.453
What is the war?

25:03.426 --> 25:05.394
The war is...

25:05.494 --> 25:06.392
Well, it's...

25:10.433 --> 25:13.402
...it's something that
shouldn't happen...

25:13.502 --> 25:14.400
...but it does.

25:16.439 --> 25:18.407
And it is when...

25:19.442 --> 25:21.410
Some people...

25:21.510 --> 25:23.410
...in another country
or any country...

25:24.447 --> 25:27.416
...try to take the lives
of other people.

25:28.451 --> 25:31.420
And then soldiers like
your daddy have to, you know...

25:31.520 --> 25:34.421
lt is my job to go over
there and stop them.

25:35.458 --> 25:38.427
