27:20.429 --> 27:22.397
l guess.

27:35.444 --> 27:38.413
We intend to convince
the Communist...

27:38.514 --> 27:41.415
...that we cannot be
defeated...

27:41.517 --> 27:43.417
...by force of arms.

27:44.453 --> 27:47.422
l have asked the
Commanding General...

27:47.523 --> 27:49.423
...General Westmoreland...

27:50.459 --> 27:52.427
...what more he needs...

27:52.528 --> 27:55.429
...to meet this mounting
aggression.

27:56.465 --> 27:58.433
He has told me.

27:59.468 --> 28:02.369
