which will raise...

28:10.479 --> 28:12.276
...our fighting strength
from 75,000 to...

28:12.448 --> 28:15.212
..1 25,000 men...

28:15.317 --> 28:17.217
...almost immediately.

28:17.319 --> 28:20.379
Additional forces will be
needed later...

28:22.424 --> 28:25.393
Get out your best dresses,
ladies.

28:26.428 --> 28:28.396
They will want to celebrate.

28:40.442 --> 28:42.410
Don't you ever...

28:42.511 --> 28:44.411
...be scared.

28:44.513 --> 28:46.413
Lean on me...

28:51.453 --> 28:54.422
l didn't hear the President
Mention a State of Emergency.

28:54.523 --> 28:55.421
No, he didn't.

28:55.524 --> 28:58.425
Well, without that declaration,
it means our enlistments...

28:58.527 --> 28:59.425
...will not be extended.

29:00.462 --> 29:01.360
l'm sorry, Hal.

29:02.398 --> 29:05.367
Forgive me, Sir, but let me
get this straight.

29:05.467 --> 29:07.367
We form a division using
techniques that...

29:07.469 --> 29:09.369
...have never been attempted
in battle...

29:09.471 --> 29:11.371
...against an enemy with 20
years of combat...

29:11.473 --> 29:13.373
...experience on his ground...

29:13.475 --> 29:16.376
