including the officers.

29:24.486 --> 29:26.386
l don't like it any better
than you do, Hal.

29:26.488 --> 29:27.386
Hell, no!

29:28.424 --> 29:31.393
You saw this coming,
didn't you...? Yes.

29:31.493 --> 29:34.394
That's why you gave me that
new crop of platoon leaders.

29:36.432 --> 29:38.400
Korea didn't teach
them anything.

29:38.500 --> 29:40.400
-Politicians?
-Politicians...

29:46.442 --> 29:47.409
Hold me.

29:48.444 --> 29:49.411
Hold me.

29:50.446 --> 29:52.414
Never let me go...

29:52.514 --> 29:54.414
...until you told me...

29:54.516 --> 29:56.416
...told me...

29:56.518 --> 29:58.418
...what l want to know...

29:58.520 --> 30:01.421
...and then just hold me.

