the units.

30:23.545 --> 30:25.445
You're now the
Commanding Officer...

30:25.547 --> 30:27.447
...of the 1 st Battalion
of the 7th Cavalry.

30:31.487 --> 30:32.454
The 7th?

30:33.489 --> 30:35.252
The same regiment
as Custer.

30:39.495 --> 30:40.462
Thank you, Sir.

30:41.497 --> 30:45.456
They told me: ''be sensible
with your love''.

30:45.567 --> 30:48.468
Don't be fooled...

30:48.570 --> 30:51.471
...they missed the last
you've find.

30:52.508 --> 30:57.468
But they never suited
after you...

30:57.579 --> 31:01.413
...when you take me in
your arms...

31:01.517 --> 31:05.419
...and l'll go slowly out of
my mind.

31:06.455 --> 31:08.423
Kiss me... kiss me.

31:09.458 --> 31:11.426
And when you do l'll know...

31:11.527 --> 31:14.428
...that you will miss me.

31:14.530 --> 31:15.428
Miss me.

31:16.465 --> 31:19.434
Did we ever say...

31:19.535 --> 31:21.435
...l've been so kiss me.

31:21.537 --> 31:22.435
Kiss me.

31:23.472 --> 31:25.440
Let me tell you...

31:25.541 --> 31:27.441
...l'm in love with you.

31:33.482 --> 31:34.449
Kiss me.

31:35.484 --> 31:37.452
Kiss me.
