31:37.553 --> 31:39.453
...that you will miss me...

32:49.491 --> 32:51.459
Look around you.

32:53.495 --> 32:55.463
ln the 7th Cavalry...

32:56.498 --> 32:58.466
...we've got a Captain from
the Ukraine...

33:00.502 --> 33:02.402
...another from Puerto Rico...

33:03.438 --> 33:06.407
...we got Japanese,
Chinese, Blacks...

33:06.508 --> 33:08.408
...Hispanics, Cherokee lndians...

33:10.445 --> 33:12.413
...Jews and Gentiles...

33:13.448 --> 33:15.416
...all Americans.

33:16.451 --> 33:18.419
Now here in the States...

33:18.520 --> 33:20.420
Some men...

33:20.522 --> 33:22.422
...in this unit...

33:22.524 --> 33:25.425
...may experience discrimination
because of race or creed.

33:26.461 --> 33:28.429
But for you and me now...

33:29.464 --> 33:31.432
...all that is gone.

33:32.467 --> 33:34.435
We're moving into
the Valley...

33:34.536 --> 33:36.436
...of the Shadow of Death.

33:37.472 --> 33:39.838
Where you will watch
the back...

33:39.942 --> 33:41.034
...of the man next to you...

33:41.143 --> 33:42.440
...as he will watch yours.

33:43.478 --> 33:45.446
And you won't care
what color he is...

33:46.481 --> 33:49.450
...or by what name
he calls God.

33:50.485 --> 33:52.453
They say we're leaving home.

33:55.490 --> 33:57.458
We're going to what home...

33:57.559 --> 33:59.459
Was always supposed to be.

34:01.430 --> 34:04.399
So let us understand
the situation.

34:05.434 --> 34:07.402
We are going into battle...

34:08.437 --> 34:11.406
...against a tough and
determined enemy.

34:15.444 --> 34:17.411
l can't promise you...

34:18.447 --> 34:21.416
...that l will bring you
all home alive.

34:23.452 --> 34:25.420
But this l swear...

34:26.455 --> 34:29.424
...before you and before
almighty God...

34:29.524 --> 34:32.425
...that when we go
into battle...

34:33.462 --> 34:36.431
...l will be the first to set
foot on the field...

34:37.466 --> 34:40.435
...and l will be the last to
step off...

34:42.471 --> 34:45.440
...and l will leave no one
behind.

34:50.478 --> 34:52.447
Dead or alive...

34:54.483 --> 34:57.452
...we will all come home
together...

34:59.488 --> 35:01.388
...so help me God.

